translations: v.繁殖，生育（procreate 的过去式和过去分词）

sentences.sentence: This means the change had procreated.
An heir to the throne was procreated.
I was born, I grew up, I studied, I loved, I married, I procreated, I said, I wrote, all gone now.
sentences.translation: 我出生，我长大，我学习，我恋爱，我结婚，我生育，我言说，我写作，如今全都成为过去。
